<h2 class="tag-line__header">

  Scheduling Made Easy</h2>
<p class="description">
  Schedule Me offers a way for clients to connect with freelancers and independent
  contractors providing an array of services.</p>

{{#link-to "professionals"}}
  {{mdl-button class="appointment-btn" isRaised=true text='Make An Appointment' isAccent=true}}
{{/link-to}}


<div class="card-row">

  {{#mdl-card class="admin-card" title='Admin' }}
    <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
      As a Freelancer or Independent Contractor you can create and organize the
      service you provide, while networking with other professionals in your field.
      Admin comes with tools that make organizing your caldendar easy,
      so you're free to spend your time doing what you do best:
      making the world more dope, one client at a time.
    </div>
    {{#link-to 'admin.detail'}}
      {{#mdl-card-actions}}
        {{mdl-button class="admin-btn" text='Admin'}}
      {{/mdl-card-actions}}
    {{/link-to}}
  {{/mdl-card}}


  {{#mdl-card class="client-card" title='Client' }}
    <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
      Find the Professional who is right for you. Schedule Me offers
      clients a place to discover a freelancer or independent contractor who
      may provide the service you seek. Clients can schedule
      appointments with your selected professional, create and maintain a personal
      page, including access to order history.
    </div>
    {{#link-to 'client.detail'}}
      {{#mdl-card-actions}}
        {{mdl-button class="client-btn" text='Client'}}
      {{/mdl-card-actions}}
    {{/link-to}}
  {{/mdl-card}}

</div>
